Subject: Re: [lm-sensors] [PATCH] I2C: i2c_bit_add_bus should initialize SDA and SCL lines
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
